<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>kubernetes on Aiden's Laboratory</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/categories/kubernetes/</link><description>Recent content in kubernetes on Aiden's Laboratory</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><copyright>Copyright © 2020-2021, Jongseob Jeon; all rights reserved.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Fri, 23 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/categories/kubernetes/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>seldon-core minikube에서 사용해보기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/minikube/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/minikube/</guid><description>
&lt;p>이번 포스트는 seldon-core를 minikube에서 사용하는 법에 대해서 설명합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;h2 id="1-install">1. Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>우선, minikube를 시작합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>minikube start
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>seldon-core를 설치할 namespace를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl create ns seldon-system
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 helm을 이용해 seldon-core를 설치합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>helm install seldon-core seldon-core-operator &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --repo https://storage.googleapis.com/seldon-charts &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --set usageMetrics.enabled&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">true&lt;/span> &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --namespace seldon-system
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>상태를 확인해 봅니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get all -n seldon-system
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>pod/seldon-controller-manager-559c567c9-9tj9w 1/1 Running &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>service/seldon-webhook-service ClusterIP 10.101.37.1 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 443/TCP 11s
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>NAME READY UP-TO-DATE AVAILABLE AGE
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>deployment.apps/seldon-controller-manager 1/1 &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>NAME DESIRED CURRENT READY AGE
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>replicaset.apps/seldon-controller-manager-559c567c9 &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span> 11s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>seldon-controller-manager pod이 정상적으로 Running 상태여야 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-sklearn-model">2. Sklearn Model&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>deploy에 이용할 모델을 만들어 보겠습니다.
모델을 생성하는 코드입니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># sklearn_model.py&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">joblib&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">load_iris&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">target&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SVC&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">fit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">joblib&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">dump&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;model.joblib&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="vm">__name__&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>실행 시켜서 &lt;code>model.joblib&lt;/code> 을 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="3-pvc">3. pvc&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>pod에 모델 파일을 옮기기 위해 pvc를 생성해야 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>우선 minikube에 접속합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>minikube ssh
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>폴더를 생성 후 종료합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>docker@minikube:~$ sudo mkdir -p /mnt/models/sklearn
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>docker@minikube:~$ &lt;span class="nb">exit&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이제 모델을 해당 경로에 넣어주어야 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>minikube cp model.joblib /mnt/models/sklearn/model.joblib
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 생성된 경로를 바라보는 pvc를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-yaml" data-lang="yaml">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c"># sklearn-pv-volume.yaml&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">PersistentVolume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sklearn-pv-volume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">labels&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">type&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">local&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storageClassName&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">manual&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">capacity&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">1Gi&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">accessModes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">ReadWriteOnce&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">hostPath&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">path&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;/mnt/models/sklearn&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nn">---&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">apiVersion&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">v1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">kind&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">PersistentVolumeClaim&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">metadata&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">name&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">sklearn-pv-volume&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">21&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">namespace&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">seldon&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">22&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">spec&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">23&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storageClassName&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">manual&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">24&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">accessModes&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">25&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>- &lt;span class="l">ReadWriteOnce&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">26&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">resources&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">27&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">requests&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">28&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="nt">storage&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w"> &lt;/span>&lt;span class="l">1Gi&lt;/span>&lt;span class="w">
&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>deploy 할 namespace를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl create ns seldon
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 &lt;code>sklearn-pv-volume.yaml&lt;/code> 를 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl apply -f sklearn-pv-volume.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>생성 후 상태를 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get pv sklearn-pv-volume
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>NAME CAPACITY ACCESS MODES RECLAIM POLICY STATUS CLAIM STORAGECLASS REASON AGE
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>sklearn-pv-volume 1Gi RWO Retain Bound seldon/sklearn-pv-volume manual 53s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="4-deploy">4. Deploy&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>이제 SeldonDeployment를 생성하겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>간단하게 SKLEARN_SERVER를 사용하는 deployment를 띄우겠습니다. 우선 아래의 내용을 &lt;code>deploy.yaml&lt;/code> 파일에 작성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># sklearn-deploy.yaml&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>apiVersion: machinelearning.seldon.io/v1
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>kind: SeldonDeployment
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>metadata:
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span> name: iris-model
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span> namespace: seldon
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>spec:
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> name: iris-model
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> predictors:
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> - graph:
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> children: &lt;span class="o">[]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> implementation: SKLEARN_SERVER
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> modelUri: pvc://sklearn-pv-volume/
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> name: classifier
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span> parameters:
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> - name: method
&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span> type: STRING
&lt;span class="ln">18&lt;/span> value: predict
&lt;span class="ln">19&lt;/span> name: default
&lt;span class="ln">20&lt;/span> replicas: &lt;span class="m">1&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 apply를 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl apply -f sklearn-deploy.yaml
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 Running이 되는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl get po -n seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME READY STATUS RESTARTS AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>iris-model-default-0-classifier-6bb64c9588-5q8ck 0/2 Running &lt;span class="m">0&lt;/span> 18s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="5-test">5. test&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>실제로 predict가 되는지 테스트를 해보겠습니다.
우선 서비스에 어떤 것들이 있는지 확인해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl get svc -n seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>NAME TYPE CLUSTER-IP EXTERNAL-IP PORT&lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>S&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span> AGE
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>iris-model-default ClusterIP 10.96.166.74 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 8000/TCP,5001/TCP 89s
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>iris-model-default-classifier ClusterIP 10.102.2.217 &amp;lt;none&amp;gt; 9000/TCP,9500/TCP 114s
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이 중 &lt;code>classifier&lt;/code> 가 붙어있는 svc 가 predict를 담당합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>로컬에서 사용할 수 있게 포트포워딩을 해줍니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl port-forward -n seldon svc/iris-model-default-classifier &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>Forwarding from 127.0.0.1:9000 -&amp;gt; &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>Forwarding from &lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>::1&lt;span class="o">]&lt;/span>:9000 -&amp;gt; &lt;span class="m">9000&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>inference할 데이터를 생성해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>다음 파일을 input.json에 저장합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;data&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">6.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">2.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">4.8&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">1.4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="mf">6.0&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">3.4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">4.5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="mf">1.6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>다음 명령어를 이용해 predict를 해봅니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; curl -H &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span> http://localhost:9000/predict -d @./input.json
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;data&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;names&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[]&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">[&lt;/span>1,1&lt;span class="o">]}&lt;/span>,&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;meta&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;requestPath&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="o">{&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;classifier&amp;#34;&lt;/span>:&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;seldonio/sklearnserver:1.7.0&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}}}&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;code>[1, 1]&lt;/code> 로 예측되어서 나오는 것을 확인할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>seldon-core local에서 사용해보기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/local/</link><pubDate>Thu, 22 Apr 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/local/</guid><description>
&lt;p>이번 포스트에서는 seldon-core를 local에서 사용하는 법에 대해서 설명합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="1-install">1. Install&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="11-seldon-core">1.1) seldon-core&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>현재 seldon-core를 로컬에서 사용하기 위해서는 multiprocessing issue로 인해 3.7에서만 가능합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>pyenv virtualenv 3.7.9 seldon
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>pyenv activate seldon
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>pip install seldon-core scikit-learn mlflow pandas
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h3 id="12-git-clone">1.2) git clone&lt;/h3>
&lt;p>local에서 사용하기 위해서는 git repo를 clone해야 합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>git clone https://github.com/SeldonIO/seldon-core
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="2-sklearn-server">2. Sklearn server&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>clone받은 repo에서 sklearn server가 위치한 경로로 이동합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> seldon-core/servers/sklearnserver/sklearnserver
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>간단한 iris를 분류하는 SVC 모델을 생성할 스크립트를 작성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># sklearn_model.py&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">joblib&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">load_iris&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">target&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SVC&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">fit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">joblib&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">dump&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;model/model.joblib&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="vm">__name__&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>모델 파일을 읽기 위해서는 경로가 필요합니다.
현재 위치를 경로로 설정할 수 없기 때문에 모델을 저장할 경로를 만듭니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>mkdir model
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그리고 위에서 작성한 스크립트를 실행해 &lt;code>model.joblib&lt;/code>을 생성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>python sklearn_model.py
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이제 서버를 실행시켜 보겠습니다. SVC 모델은 predict 함수만 있기 때문에 parameter에서 predict method를 주겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>seldon-core-microservice SKLearnServer --parameters &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;[{&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;method&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;type&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;STRING&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;value&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;predict&amp;#34;}, {&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;model_uri&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;STRING&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;value&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;file://model/&amp;#34;}]&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이제 predict를 해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl -H &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span> http://localhost:9000/predict -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;data&amp;#34;:{
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;: [[0.6745011455,-0.5923730118, 1.0469454037, 1.1855672065]],
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;names&amp;#34;: [&amp;#34;sepal length (cm)&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;sepal width (cm)&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;petal length (cm)&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;petal width (cm)&amp;#34;]
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> },
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;meta&amp;#34; : {}
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="3-mlflow-server">3. MLflow server&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>clone받은 repo에서 mlflow server가 위치한 경로로 이동합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> seldon-core/servers/sklearnserver/sklearnserver
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>mlflow를 이용해 모델을 저장할 스크립트를 작성합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-python" data-lang="python">&lt;span class="ln"> 1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="c1"># mlflow_model.py&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">mlflow&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">mlflow.models.signature&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">infer_signature&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kn">from&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nn">sklearn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kn">import&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 6&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">():&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">datasets&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">load_iris&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln"> 9&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">df&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">target&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">10&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">svm&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">SVC&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">12&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">fit&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">y&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">13&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">signature&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">infer_signature&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">predict&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">X&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">))&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">14&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">mlflow&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">sklearn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">log_model&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">clf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;iris_model&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">signature&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">signature&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">15&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">16&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">if&lt;/span> &lt;span class="vm">__name__&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">==&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;__main__&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">17&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">train&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>스크립트를 실행시키면 mlrus 폴더가 생성됩니다.
생성된 mlruns 폴더에서 artifact의 모델 경로를 찾습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">cd&lt;/span> mlruns/0/d96ad56315364063901ace2df62dfbc2/artifacts/iris_model
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; ls
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>MLmodel conda.yaml model.pkl
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이제 서버를 실행시켜 보겠습니다. mlflow 서버는 predict 함수만을 지원합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>seldon-core-microservice MLFlowServer --parameters &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;[{&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;model_uri&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;type&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;STRING&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;value&amp;#34;: &amp;#34;file://mlruns/0/d96ad56315364063901ace2df62dfbc2/artifacts/iris_model/&amp;#34;}]&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>이제 predict를 해보겠습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>curl -H &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;Content-Type: application/json&amp;#34;&lt;/span> http://localhost:9000/predict -d &lt;span class="s1">&amp;#39;{
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;data&amp;#34;:{
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;ndarray&amp;#34;: [[0.6745011455,-0.5923730118, 1.0469454037, 1.1855672065]],
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;names&amp;#34;: [&amp;#34;sepal length (cm)&amp;#34;, &amp;#34;sepal width (cm)&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;petal length (cm)&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;petal width (cm)&amp;#34;]
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> },
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1"> &amp;#34;meta&amp;#34; : {}
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s1">}&amp;#39;&lt;/span>
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>kubernetes에서 ghcr package pull 하기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Mar 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/kubernetes/kubernetes_ghcr/</guid><description>
&lt;p>kubernetes 에서 사용하는 image는 기본적으로 dockerhub에서 pull 된다. 기본적으로 Local에 있는 패키지는 사용하지 않는다.
회사에서는 도커 이미지를 dockerhub와 같은 곳에 public 하게 공유할 수가 없다.
그래서 github 에서 제공하는 (GHCR) GitHub Container Registry for Docker images 을 이용해서 도커 이미지를 관리하고 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>GHCR 을 이용하기 위해서는 github access key 가 필요하다. 우선 github access token을 발급 받아 보자.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="1-ghcr-을-위한-github-access-token-발급-받기">1. ghcr 을 위한 github access token 발급 받기&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>우선 github setting에서 deplotver settings / personal access tokens 로 들어간다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/0.png" alt="그림-1">
여기서 generate new token을 누른다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/1.png" alt="그림-2">
토큰 이름으로 ghcr-token을 입력하고 packages와 관련된 권한을 주고 token을 생성한다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/k8s/ghcr/2.png" alt="그림-3">
다음과 같이 토큰이 생성된다. 이제 이 토큰을 잘 저장해둔다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="2-kubernetes-secret">2. kubernetes secret&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>다음으로 kubernetes 에 secret 을 생성해준다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>kubectl -n &amp;lt;k8s-namespace&amp;gt; create secret docker-registry &amp;lt;k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-username&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;email-address&amp;gt;
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;code>k8s-docker-registry-secret-name&lt;/code>: secret 이름&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-username&lt;/code>: github 유저 네임&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>github-personal-access-token&lt;/code>: 발급받은 토큰&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;code>email-address&lt;/code>: github 이메일&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>예를 들면 아래와 같이 사용할 수 있다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>&amp;gt; kubectl -n default create secret docker-registry test-ghcr &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-server&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ghcr.io &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-username&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>aiden-jeon &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-password&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>&amp;lt;github-personal-access-token&amp;gt; &lt;span class="se">\
&lt;/span>&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span>&lt;span class="se">&lt;/span> --docker-email&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>ells2124@gmail.com
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>정상적으로 실행될 경우 아래와 같이 출력된다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>secret/test-ghcr created
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="3-yaml-파일-작성">3. yaml 파일 작성&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>이제 deployment를 위한 yaml 파일을 작성한다.&lt;/p>
